snippet.title: Louisiana Beer Reviews: Abita Amber (duo review)
snippet.description:
4.5% alcohol. 17 IBU. Introduced in 1986. Brewed in Louisiana by Abita Brewing. 

"Amber Lager is a Munich style lager brewed with pale and caramel malts and German Perle hops. It has a smooth, malty, slightly caramel flavor and a rich amber color. Abita Amber was the first beer offered by the brewery and continues to be our leading seller. Amber Lager is Abita‚Äôs most versatile beer for pairing with food. It has been voted "best beer" in numerous New Orleans reader polls and is used frequently in recipes of great Louisiana chefs."

https://abita.com/brews/abita-amber#

Ingredients
Alaskan Amber is made from glacier-fed water and a generous blend of the finest quality European and Pacific Northwest hop varieties and premium two-row pale and specialty malts. Flavor
Richly malty and long on the palate, with just enough hop backing to make this beautiful amber colored ‚Äúalt‚Äù style beer notably well balanced.

snippet.title: Mold review and faux amber tutorial
snippet.description:
This video is a review of molds I got from barsikmoy etsy shop. in the video I said these molds were from Russia, they are not. Those are other molds I'm waiting on to do a review of. I highly recommend these molds.     The only let down was the not glossy finish when I pulled the molds out but that was an easy fix. please visit my etsy page and like my Facebook and Instagram pages for more updates.
https://www.etsy.com/shop/ColesCrochetStore
https://www.facebook.com/colescrochetstore/
https://instagram.com/coles_crochet_and_woodcrafts?igshid=1a2t46j7oo90n

https://www.etsy.com/listing/676813375/silicon-mold-cabochons-irregular-shape

To get the high gloss shine I was looking for I used hutt ultra gloss finish. here is the link for that.
https://www.woodcraft.com/products/hut-ultra-gloss-plastic-polish

The resin I like to use is amazing clear cast resin by allumite. it's my favorite resin for doing things that will be dyed because it can get a little yellow with time. here is the link.

the dye I use for all of my coloring that isn't alcohol ink is this.

heat gun

the UV resin I use 
https://amzn.to/3bygtVr

and the UV light
https://amzn.to/33PVlr9

snippet.title: Aquaman = Movie Review 2018 = Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Yahya Abdul-Mateen
snippet.description:
‚ÄúAquaman‚Äù is a 2018 superhero movie about a man of royal blood that was born outside of the borders of his parent's native country. That country is very secluded and has exotic, advanced technology beyond anything in the rest of the modern world is aware of. There are factions within the country that believe a conflict with the outside world is not only inevitable, but their country should rule the because of its biological and technological superiority. The man of royal blood decides to journey to the reclusive nations and challenge for the throne of the kingdom in order to lead its people into a new geopolitical future. 

If that read like the premise of ‚ÄúBlack Panther‚Äù, then you'd be correct. The newest DCEU movie is very similar to multiple super hero and science fantasy films of recent times, and I make references to those similarities throughout this YouTube video. I also offered a grade of B+ (with reluctant bias), which is explained within the presentation. Strap yourselves in. Batten down the hatches. There are some rough waters ahead.

The movie was directed by James Wan. It stars Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Willem Dafoe, Patrick Wilson, Dolph Lundgren, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Nicole Kidman, Temuera Morrison, Randall Park, Graham McTavish, Ludi Lin, Michael Beach, Leigh Whannell, Djimon Hounsou, and Julie Andrews.

snippet.title: AMBER TEETHING NECKLACE REVIEW!! | Baby Amber Teething Necklace
snippet.description:
Do amber teething necklaces perform up to their hype? My son has been using an amber teething necklace since he was about a month old and I can't talk more positively about it. I LOVE THIS NECKLACE!! I never would have thought that this necklace would actually work but it does.

How it works? The necklace is made of pure amber which when heated up by the skin releases a natural inflammatory and pain reliever. This is why it is used so much with babies who are teething. I found that the necklace helped Nolan with his slobber more than anything. He would slobber through an entire outfit so quickly before he wore this necklace. It did help him with pain I believe. There is really no way of knowing since he can't talk to us however the lack of slobber was AMAZING!! 

I call this necklace a miracle worker because within 24 hours he was a totally different baby. Try this necklace out for yourself and see if it helps your baby. Every baby is different and every necklace is different. Find the right size and color for your baby and you will fall in love with the teething necklace just like I have!!

snippet.title: Aquaman Spoiler Review
snippet.description:
Aquaman directed by James Wan and starring Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Nicole Kidman, Patrick Wilson, Willem Dafoe, Temeura Morrison and Dolph Lundgren swims out to sea this holiday season. The film professes to be an action-packed adventure that spans the vast, visually breathtaking underwater world of the seven seas. The film reveals the origin story of half-human, half-Atlantean Arthur Curry and takes him on the journey of his lifetime‚Äîone that will not only force him to face who he really is, but to discover if he is worthy of who he was born to be‚Ä¶a king.

Kristian Harloff, Perri Nemiroff, Denniz Tzeng and Dorian Parks are here to give you their SPOILER filled review of the film. They look at the action, direction, special effects, visuals and storylines of the movie. They let you know what worked for them in the film and what did not. They also let you know if this is part of the new direction for DC. Let us know what you thought of the movie in the Comments section below. snippet.title: Aquaman Tamil - Nathan's Movie Review | James Wan | Jason Momoa | Amber Heard | Future Talks |
snippet.description:
Aquaman is a 2018 American superhero film based on the DC Comics character of the same name, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is the sixth installment in the DC Extended Universe (DCEU). Directed by James Wan, with a screenplay by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick and Will Beall, from a story by Geoff Johns, Wan, and Beall, it stars Jason Momoa as the title character, with Amber Heard, Willem Dafoe, Patrick Wilson, Dolph Lundgren, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, and Nicole Kidman in supporting roles. It is the third live-action theatrical film featuring Aquaman, following Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice (2016) and Justice League (2017), and the first full-length feature film centered around the character. In Aquaman, Arthur Curry, the heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, must step forward to lead his people against his half-brother, Orm, who seeks to unite the seven underwater kingdoms against the surface world.

snippet.title: Amber Heard's Miami wonderland at the¬†Delano hotel  - Travel Guide vs Booking
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching, Like, shre , comment vs Subscribe Please!
 Continuing our series on the world‚Äôs hottest hotels and the stars who frequent them, this week Sarah Turner checks out the Delano in Miami‚Ä¶Vital statistics:¬†Designed by Robert Swartburg and named after the then US President, Franklin Delano Roosevelt, the Art Deco turrets of the Delano have dominated South Beach since it opened in 1947.In 1994, famed hotelier and nightclub owner Ian Schrager took the helm. With designer Philippe Starck, and using contemporary art and a party vibe, he invented this cool and aspirational boutique hotel.The 194 all-white bedrooms are so plain they could pass for a posh hospital, but they‚Äôre designed to drive people into public spaces for entertainment such as the Argentinian-tinged restaurant Leynia, or the small but chic Doheny Room, which aims for an indie 1980s club feel.Is the Delano pretentious? Yes, a little. Most hotels in Miami have a swimming pool, but the Delano has decreed that it has a water salon because most of the pool is designed to be shallow enough for guests to wade in at chest height while sipping cocktails, but it is a great deal of fun.Location report: At the corner of Collins and 17th Street, this is where South Beach‚Äôs hotels become bigger and ‚Äì crucially ‚Äì have gates that lead straight on to the beach.The Delano is surrounded by a clutch of luxury hotels, including SLS and The Raleigh.A tall hedge separates it from the street and keeps gawkers away. Key attraction: When Ian Schrager took over the Delano, he wanted to make hotels as exciting as nightclubs.It still takes fun very seriously. Starck looked to Alice In Wonderland for inspiration.The garden is filled with fairy lights, daybeds and giant chessboards. The pool bungalows ‚Äì adored by A-listers such as Leonardo DiCaprio ‚Äì are the most popular.Inside, the lobby continues the spectacle with a clear grand piano which is played, when the mood takes her, by Queen Latifah.In the news: The Delano is no longer quite as cutting-edge, but it still has a vibe that other hotels envy.The weekend pool parties have become a South Beach institution; giant inflatables and a DJ playing by the bar so that guests don‚Äôt have to leave their sunlounger.It still attracts celebrity guests ‚Äì last year Johnny Depp‚Äôs ex Amber Heard checked in.Good enough for the rest of us?If you‚Äôre not staying there, the all-you-can-eat brunch is a South Beach bargain at $70 (about ¬£53) a head, with unlimited mimosas or Bloody Marys for just $15 (¬£11) more.
